Parse listing urls

Parses a vector of listing urls

parse_listing_urls(urls = NULL, include_features = F, sleep_time = 1,
  return_message = TRUE)

Arguments

urls

vector of urls
include_features

if TRUE includes features
sleep_time

sleep time in between url
return_message

if TRUE returns a message

Value

a data_frame
